# Dependencies

## Core Dependencies

| Package | Version | Role | Upgrade Risk |
|---|---|---|---|
| next | 13.4.10-canary.2 | Framework | HIGH — pages router changes, edge runtime |
| react / react-dom | 18.2.0 | UI | HIGH — React 19 is a major shift |
| mongodb | 6.6.2 | Database driver | MEDIUM — query API changes |
| iron-session | 6.1.3 | Auth sessions | MEDIUM — API changed significantly in v8 |
| stripe | 15.10.0 | Payments | MEDIUM — large version gap to v22 |

